## Write invariants (normative)

1. All [T1] sections must reflect current state before setting `RunStatus = paused`.
2. All [T1] sections must reflect current state before changing `RunStage`.
3. [T2] sections are best-effort — a crash mid-T2 write does not corrupt resumability.
4. **Gap parameters + R2 target assignments** is write-once. Never edited after R1→R2 hand-off.
5. **Round 2 subagent roster** section must exist (even empty) before first R2 subagent spawns.
6. **Deduplication log** written even when zero duplicates found.
7. **Per-doc ingestion status** rows written at upload, not at ingestion trigger.
